Top 10 canonical pathways. Table showing the top 10 canonical pathways to which all genes with a p-value of less than 0.001 during Makona infection were aligned in Ingenuity Pathway Analysis. Log p-value is shown as an indication of confidence in the functional grouping. Genes aligned to each pathway are functionally related and are connected either indirectly or directly to other components of the pathway.
